1
00:01:11,051 --> 00:01:12,091
What's the use of you?

2
00:01:12,461 --> 00:01:13,711
You can save nothing

3
00:01:14,011 --> 00:01:15,551
If anything happens to Her Majesty,

4
00:01:15,711 --> 00:01:17,130
none of you can survive

5
00:01:17,131 --> 00:01:18,301
I deserve death

6
00:01:18,301 --> 00:01:19,591
A bunch of trash

7
00:02:09,881 --> 00:02:10,671
Your Highness

8
00:02:11,011 --> 00:02:13,011
Eunuch Ai and Lord Song have been arrested

9
00:02:13,261 --> 00:02:14,421
Our spies

10
00:02:14,421 --> 00:02:15,841
were all cleared by Lord Xue

11
00:02:15,881 --> 00:02:18,761
And all our shops in the capital were sealed

12
00:02:18,961 --> 00:02:21,301
Her Majesty is not leaving us a way to live

13
00:02:22,011 --> 00:02:24,761
Your Highness, we have to plan ahead

14
00:02:27,671 --> 00:02:29,011
The Empress is unworthy of her position

15
00:02:29,551 --> 00:02:31,671
She treated you like this just for a man

16
00:02:32,171 --> 00:02:34,461
Are you going to wait until she kills you first?

17
00:02:36,841 --> 00:02:37,801
I have my own plans

18
00:02:50,921 --> 00:02:52,011
Report

19
00:02:58,171 --> 00:02:58,631
Report

20
00:02:59,001 --> 00:03:01,011
The Second Prince has raised an army to rebel. What?

21
00:03:01,171 --> 00:03:02,461
He proclaims himself emperor a hundred miles away

22
00:03:02,841 --> 00:03:04,211
The rebels are almost at the southern outskirts of the capital

23
00:03:08,921 --> 00:03:09,761
I can help you

24
00:03:14,511 --> 00:03:16,011
The Second Prince daring to quickly claim the throne

25
00:03:16,131 --> 00:03:17,921
shows he's been scheming for a long time

26
00:03:18,011 --> 00:03:19,881
Yes, the death of the late emperor,

27
00:03:19,881 --> 00:03:21,011
although the prince took the blame,

28
00:03:21,211 --> 00:03:23,171
we all know it was the Second Prince who masterminded it

29
00:03:23,261 --> 00:03:24,671
We just never had the evidence

30
00:03:25,011 --> 00:03:26,001
He did it very cleanly

31
00:03:27,341 --> 00:03:28,960
This time the rebels came so quickly

32
00:03:29,841 --> 00:03:31,880
We will definitely not be able to muster all our forces in time

33
00:03:32,211 --> 00:03:33,051
Logically,

34
00:03:33,261 --> 00:03:34,211
the army must be stationed in

35
00:03:34,211 --> 00:03:35,671
the uninhabited area hundreds of miles away

36
00:03:35,801 --> 00:03:37,301
I have sent people to light the beacon tower

37
00:03:37,301 --> 00:03:39,341
But before the reinforcements arrive,

38
00:03:39,671 --> 00:03:40,711
we need to hold out on our own

39
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,630
Let's use a ploy of camouflage

40
00:03:49,211 --> 00:03:51,131
I'll have people dress scarecrows

41
00:03:51,671 --> 00:03:53,551
in these prominent high spots

42
00:03:54,301 --> 00:03:55,631
so the enemy

43
00:03:56,261 --> 00:03:58,961
thinks there are guards in the city

44
00:03:59,011 --> 00:04:01,801
That way, they'll be less likely to act recklessly

45
00:04:03,461 --> 00:04:04,001
Come

46
00:04:07,131 --> 00:04:07,801
Wuming

47
00:04:08,011 --> 00:04:08,631
Yes

48
00:04:08,671 --> 00:04:10,051
You, as the first line of defense,

49
00:04:10,301 --> 00:04:11,761
gather all the troops and confront the enemy

50
00:04:11,761 --> 00:04:14,341
in the southern outskirts to wear them down

51
00:04:16,421 --> 00:04:18,631
Fei, you, as the second line of defense,

52
00:04:19,011 --> 00:04:20,421
if Wuming can't hold them off,

53
00:04:21,301 --> 00:04:22,670
gather all the female troops

54
00:04:23,711 --> 00:04:24,591
and provide timely support

55
00:04:26,131 --> 00:04:26,761
Okay

56
00:04:27,671 --> 00:04:30,001
I will swear to defend the palace and protect Hong Dou

57
00:04:30,461 --> 00:04:31,211
with the Imperial Guards to the death

58
00:04:34,841 --> 00:04:36,460
We'll wait for the reinforcements together

59
00:04:39,051 --> 00:04:40,091
Swear to defend the Southern Kingdom to the death

60
00:04:54,461 --> 00:04:55,961
Why are you still playing at this time?

61
00:04:56,461 --> 00:04:57,551
Let's play together

62
00:04:57,551 --> 00:04:57,961
Childish

63
00:04:58,131 --> 00:04:58,841
Let me have a try

64
00:04:58,881 --> 00:05:00,091
Stop it, hurry up

65
00:05:00,341 --> 00:05:01,170
Okay, okay

66
00:05:02,421 --> 00:05:03,211
That's too late

67
00:05:04,131 --> 00:05:04,710
Lend a hand

68
00:05:05,011 --> 00:05:06,001
Come! Come here quickly!

69
00:05:11,921 --> 00:05:12,341
Quickly!

70
00:05:13,131 --> 00:05:14,511
Come on, everyone, work harder

71
00:05:15,011 --> 00:05:15,421
Hurry up

72
00:05:37,001 --> 00:05:37,881
Wake up!

73
00:05:38,261 --> 00:05:39,131
Wake up!

74
00:05:39,551 --> 00:05:40,511
The Southern Kingdom is in trouble

75
00:05:40,591 --> 00:05:42,001
The Southern Kingdom needs you

76
00:05:42,711 --> 00:05:44,341
Hong Dou! Hong Dou!

77
00:05:45,551 --> 00:05:46,420
Wake up!

78
00:05:46,881 --> 00:05:48,460
Wake up, Hong Dou!

79
00:06:01,881 --> 00:06:04,511
Chen, why aren't we staying safely in the palace?

80
00:06:05,341 --> 00:06:07,001
Why are we here causing trouble?

81
00:06:08,011 --> 00:06:08,591
Xulai

82
00:06:09,001 --> 00:06:11,841
If we wait until the rebels break into the palace, we'll have lost

83
00:06:12,631 --> 00:06:14,460
I still think it's better to see things for ourselves

84
00:06:15,011 --> 00:06:16,511
Who knows, we might be able to help

85
00:06:16,841 --> 00:06:18,091
Chen is right

86
00:06:18,091 --> 00:06:19,210
Fuck right!

87
00:06:19,301 --> 00:06:21,211
Didn't we say we would go to the palace together and enjoy happiness?

88
00:06:21,261 --> 00:06:22,631
Where is the happiness?

89
00:06:22,711 --> 00:06:24,091
There is no happiness at all

90
00:06:24,131 --> 00:06:25,710
And we almost lost our lives

91
00:06:28,671 --> 00:06:29,461
Women

92
00:06:29,881 --> 00:06:31,011
A group of women

93
00:06:31,461 --> 00:06:32,461
Let's go

94
00:06:36,211 --> 00:06:38,381
Fei, long time no see

95
00:06:41,301 --> 00:06:42,511
The palace defenses are already in place

96
00:06:42,511 --> 00:06:44,341
We're here to see if there's anything we can do to help

97
00:06:45,131 --> 00:06:46,011
Report

98
00:06:46,881 --> 00:06:48,301
Bad news—our forces are losing ground,

99
00:06:48,341 --> 00:06:49,511
and General Xue has been injured

100
00:06:50,301 --> 00:06:52,461
Got it. Send reinforcements immediately! Yes

101
00:06:53,301 --> 00:06:54,961
How about we leave first?

102
00:06:54,961 --> 00:06:55,841
Go! Go! Go!

103
00:06:58,421 --> 00:07:00,511
Wait for me! Wait for me!

104
00:07:00,711 --> 00:07:01,341
Hurry up!

105
00:07:16,001 --> 00:07:17,341
So cool!

106
00:07:28,591 --> 00:07:29,710
It's my woman
